ri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974652_519462803978661_5861237216833818903_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=z7xrPRPPRiYQ7kNvgEExK23&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCpUsB4KyIkuApA3HwCXb1cHlhBI8stA8ErqxeIeqMp2Q&oe=676A9F3C"}, {"file_name": "Untitled-7.png", "id": "379966851375388", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982555_379966854708721_6237733781365760945_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=aRb-yahFnvUQ7kNvgHwyAHm&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDCFdt0p--dl0xzWBZqWq6VGSWPgrXmHQONUg9LfTpOpg&oe=676A90D7"}, {"file_name": "Untitled-3.png", "id": "1457878311765107", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75647714_1457878321765106_873955209399552846_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=m6MW3GDVgRIQ7kNvgGhjuPy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAgLzckgCp2TBopsfNXwaMsywX6Te01s7UNkTADDDZ9Xw&oe=676A8406"}, {"file_name": "Untitled-2.png", "id": "853176473329833", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75196224_853176476663166_2779387245026015972_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mZo7j_994QQQ7kNvgGRtn1i&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCuz-J2ZenNewBDwiTq_NzQUbaHsGij0mYBmQlGP4Qz-A&oe=676AA1C3"}, {"file_name": "Untitled-6.png", "id": "838588491102212", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031309_838588494435545_3221430962329902390_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=euCJVS64S64Q7kNvgGGLhOP&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDeuAbvmIlrwQbbTIiHqqVKcPVnvcYnHTkd5Uj3GGPVUA&oe=676AA392"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "WIZARD.S.LEGACY.COVER.24.BIT (1).png", "id": "794564832812199", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/65228545_794564836145532_348548685399172447_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=h6XcWhr6TksQ7kNvgEpHh2A&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCt3YzoTx4dz1sMujJ6GoT5VW7c4L0qXaGxQ1bhXIgiNQ&oe=676A9422"}, "display_name": "Wizard's Legacy", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Wizard\u2019s Legacy blends VR immersion with roguelite replayability, offering action, adventure, and fantasy. Play as a powerful wizard, explore dynamic dungeons, face formidable foes, and uncover ancient secrets. Become the wizard you were meant to be.\n\n{3648923568693208}\nA desperate father, bound by a dark pact, transforms into a wizard trapped within a cursed labyrinth. Each victory grants power, but death returns him to the start. Explore the labyrinth's ever-changing depths, where every battle unveils its grim history. Can you master magic, overcome enemies, and save your child?\n\n{362183290313011}\n\n{459743683357113}\nDive deeper, shaping the world with every decision. Explore branching paths, unearth secrets, and face escalating challenges. Collect potions and power-ups scattered throughout to enhance your magic and forge your destiny as a powerful wizard.\n\n{828863472676196}\nUnleash your inner wizard! Draw symbols to control fireballs, ice walls, and lightning. Feel the power surge as you master arcane combat.\n\n{1407283433268429}\n\n{1453454962100883}\nChoose from a variety of playable characters, each with unique spells and abilities. Experiment with different playstyles \u2013 fiery mage, cunning illusionist, or something else entirely?\n\n{1136617717392676}\nThe labyrinth teems with cunning foes, each demanding a unique strategy. Test your skills against a diverse array of enemies, adapting tactics to exploit weaknesses and emerge victorious.\n\n{788110426812574}\n\n{1584321828806767}\nImmerse yourself in stunning visuals. Explore dynamic dungeons, lush forests, and ominous landscapes, each meticulously detailed for an unforgettable VR experience.\n\n\n{1415112652482029}\n\n", "short_description": "Wizard\u2019s Legacy blends VR immersion with roguelite replayability,